@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container my-5">
    <h1 class="text-center fw-bold">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-center lead">Dedicated to rescuing, rehabilitating, and rehoming pets while promoting responsible pet ownership.</p>

    <div class="mt-5">
        <h3>🐾 Who We Are</h3>
        <p>We are a passionate team of animal lovers working to provide shelter, medical care, and adoption services for homeless and neglected pets. Our goal is to create a world where every pet has a safe and loving home.</p>

        <h3>🏡 Why Adopt?</h3>
        <p>Adopting a pet saves lives. Every year, millions of pets end up in shelters, waiting for a second chance. By adopting, you help reduce pet overpopulation and give an animal a loving home.</p>

        <h4>✅ Benefits of Adopting:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Gives a pet a second chance at life</li>
            <li>Reduces demand for unethical breeding practices</li>
            <li>Most adopted pets are already vaccinated and trained</li>
            <li>Promotes a compassionate and responsible pet culture</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>📚 Responsible Pet Ownership</h3>
        <p>Being a pet owner comes with important responsibilities. Here are some key aspects of responsible pet care:</p>

        <h4>🩺 Health & Wellness</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Regular veterinary checkups and vaccinations</li>
            <li>Spaying and neutering to prevent overpopulation</li>
            <li>Providing a nutritious diet and regular exercise</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>💖 Love & Commitment</h4>
        <ul>
            <li>Ensuring a safe and loving home environment</li>
            <li>Providing training and socialization</li>
            <li>Committing to lifelong care</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>🌍 How You Can Help</h3>
        <p>There are many ways to support animal welfare and help us continue our mission:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Adopt a pet from a shelter instead of buying</li>
            <li>Volunteer at animal shelters and rescue organizations</li>
            <li>Donate to support food, medical care, and shelter operations</li>
            <li>Spread awareness about responsible pet ownership</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
        <h3>Join Our Mission</h3>
        <p>Ready to make a difference? Whether you want to adopt, volunteer, or donate, your support helps save lives.</p>
        <a href="/Pet/Index" class="btn btn-primary">Adopt a Pet</a>
        <a href="/Volunteer" class="btn btn-warning">Become a Volunteer</a>
        
    </div>
</div>
